{"tid":572254,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無乜壞事發生都好似唔開心咁嘅？","createTime":"2018-02-25T12:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T14:56:17.000Z","uid":37196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"52f87f3ad294c021eabe00175556bc1d2dac2d99","tid":572254,"uid":37196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"就三張，和平分手咗幾個月，朋友唔多約出街，嗜好都無乜，返新工都係幾個月，之前peak season 要chur埋星期六日，而家無咁忙星期六日無所事事。<br />\n<br />\n生活唔算多壞事，但又好似無咩事值得開心、或者真正由心而發嘅開心。有時無啦啦都會醒起自己無嘢好開心。<br />\n<br />\n係咪搵啲嘢學下，搵個目標俾自己，咁就會容易開心啲？"},{"pid":"106532f50d39262be77a1f26672396ba17d84785","tid":572254,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:07:19.000Z","msg":"我點知你點先開心 問自己<br />\n做你鍾意做既野"},{"pid":"ec4994d854a997c4a7e6c48a9cddba1d53a057ca","tid":572254,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"情緒或高或低如此詭秘"},{"pid":"f8e5b6913d62fea7e5a32006ff60548858a9d8cc","tid":572254,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:19:43.000Z","msg":"因為唔慣掛"},{"pid":"015979ae70b9fb2d3a112e42b70f28db41560027","tid":572254,"uid":37196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"106532f50d39262be77a1f26672396ba17d84785","tid":572254,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:07:19.000Z","msg":"我點知你點先開心 問自己<br />\n做你鍾意做既野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"請教下你個人嚟講做咩事會開心啲？定係呢個唔算開心嘅狀態其實其他人都會有？"},{"pid":"2df0f52ac7afd61266914b6180e893fc83d7eeda","tid":572254,"uid":37196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec4994d854a997c4a7e6c48a9cddba1d53a057ca","tid":572254,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"情緒或高或低如此詭秘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"呢隻歌叫卓韻芝唔好自殺，好彩我無自殺嘅諗法"},{"pid":"bd48a151ab3c5680a806ec737e69c15ecaae2f33","tid":572254,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"